summary: A small mod that adds a new Orc hold not too far from Sleeping Tree Camp.
descriptionHtml:
Sorry about the dead-ness of this mod, hopefully I can get a bit more done in the next few days, maybe I\'ll finish it someday, thanks to all the people who still actually want to see this finshed.

This mod adds a new Orc Hold to the Whiterun Plains, near Sleeping Tree Camp that includes a player owned Longhouse with a bed, plenty of storage, an Enchanting Table and an Alchemy Table and a Cooking Spit. 

The exterior includes a full Blacksmith set (Tanning Rack, Smelter, etc.) as well as a Goat pen and some farmland.

NPCs may be added at a later date.

I have added the file to the Nexus that includes the fort itself, the old version only included the Longhouse interior.
author: SledgePopadopalos
